#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/centaur.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Athletics +6, Perception +3, Survival +3    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 13    \n"
"**Languages** Elvish, Sylvan    \n"
"**Challenge** 2 (450 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/centaur.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Charge.** If the centaur moves at least 30 feet straight toward a target "
"and then hits it with a pike attack on the same turn, the target takes an "
"extra 10 (3d6) piercing damage. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/centaur.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Multiattack.** The centaur makes two attacks: one with its pike and one "
"with its hooves or two with its longbow.    \n"
"**Pike.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"9 (1d10 + 4) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Hooves.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 11 (2d6 + 4) bludgeoning damage.    \n"
"**Longbow.** _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, range 150/600 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage.\n"
msgstr ""
